Fishing pole trap. Need hook, bait and fish that bites. }
1. e4 e5 (1... c5 { Sicilian } 2. Nf3 e6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 a6 5. Nc3 Qc7 6. Be2 Nf6 7. O-O h5 8. Be3 (8. Bg5) 8... Ng4 9. Bxg4 hxg4 10. Qxg4 (10. g3 b5 11. Qxg4 Bb7) 10... Qxh2#) 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 Nf6 { Berlin defence } 4. O-O Ng4 { N is bait } (4... Nxe4 { main line, only a temporary pawn win. }) 5. h3 (5. Re1 Bc5 6. d4 Nxd4 7. Nxd4 (7. Be3) 7... Qh4 8. Nf3 Qxf2+ 9. Kh1 Qg1+ 10. Rxg1 Nf2#) 5... h5 { h5 is hook } 6. hxg4 { hxg4 bites } 6... hxg4 7. Ne1 Qh4 8. f4 g3 9. Qh5 Rxh5 10. Nf3 Qh1# *

